msgid ""
"Your session has expired. Please remove and re-add your account in "
"Preferences."
msgstr ""
"Sessionen er udløbet. Kontoen skal slettes og tilføjes igen i Indstillinger."

#: core/Services/CalDAV/Core.vala:332
msgid "Too Many Requests"
msgstr "For mange requests"

