msgid "The request failed due to a server error."
msgstr "Requesten mislykkedes pga. serverfejl."

#: core/Services/Todoist/Todoist.vala:600 src/Widgets/ErrorView.vala:194
msgid "The server is currently unable to handle the request."
msgstr "Serveren kan ikke behandle requesten lige nu."

